== 迴響 ==

=== 評價 ===
《行動代號：華爾奇麗雅》收穫了普遍影評人的好評。根據[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]上收集的193篇專業影評文章，其中119篇給出了「新鮮」的正面評價，「新鮮度」為62%，平均得分6.1分（滿分10分）<ref name="rt">{{cite web | url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/valkyrie/ | title=Valkyrie Movie Reviews | publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] | accessdate=2011-12-14 | archive-date=2016-05-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160524183401/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/valkyrie | dead-url=no }}</ref>，而基於另一影評網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的40篇評論文章，其中19篇予以好評，1篇差評，16篇褒貶不一，平均分為56（滿分100）<ref name="meta">{{cite web | url=http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/valkyrie | title=Valkyrie (2008): Reviews | publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] | accessdate=2009-01-21 | archive-date=2010-03-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100313172422/http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/valkyrie | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在美國，該電影獲得了影評人褒貶不一的評價<ref name="meta"/><ref name="itzkoff">{{cite news | last=Itzkoff | first=David | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/12/30/arts/30arts-GERMANYHOSPI_BRF.html | title=Germany Hospitable to Cruise's 'Valkyrie' | work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] | date=2008-12-29 | accessdate=2008-12-29 | archive-date=2019-11-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191106235342/https://www.nytimes.com/2008/12/30/arts/30arts-GERMANYHOSPI_BRF.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
電影於2009年1月20日在歐洲上映，地點選擇在[[柏林|柏林]]的[[波茨坦广场|波茨坦廣場]]舉行<ref name="dw">{{cite news | url=http://www.dw-world.de/dw/article/0,,3960359,00.html | title=Tom Cruise's Anti-Hitler Hero Draws Mixed Reviews in Germany | publisher=[[Deutsche_Welle|Deutsche Welle]] | date=2009-01-20 | accessdate=2009-01-24 | archive-date=2012-01-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120124014110/http://www.dw-world.de/dw/article/0,,3960359,00.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。1月23日於美國及加拿大以外的十多個地區發行<ref name="tops">{{cite journal | last=McNary | first=Dave | url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117999034.html?categoryid=13&cs=1&nid=2564 | title='Valkyrie' tops foreign box office | journal=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date=2009-01-25 | accessdate=2009-01-27 | archive-date=2009-02-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090226103712/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117999034.html?categoryid=13&cs=1&nid=2564 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="overseas">{{cite journal|url=http://hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/news/e3ic96aa80f511fb30fd5f44b20accfde91 |title='Valkyrie,' 'Slumdog' strong overseas |journal=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=2009-01-25 |accessdate=2009-01-27 |archivedate=2009-01-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090130063319/http://hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/news/e3ic96aa80f511fb30fd5f44b20accfde91 }}</ref>，其中包括1月22日的德國<ref name="roxborough" />。首映週末，電影收入在德國、澳大利亞和荷蘭位居第一，而在英國、奧地利與韓國位居第二。其中票房收入最高的國家為德國，電影從689家劇院賺取了370萬美元的票房，平均每家劇院收益5,311美元<ref name="roxborough">{{cite journal | last=Roxborough | first=Scott | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/film/news/e3i5f45653915ac1124156cd32ccc756437 | title=German critics come around on 'Valkyrie' | journal=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] | date=2008-12-18 | accessdate=2008-12-24 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081221094339/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/film/news/e3i5f45653915ac1124156cd32ccc756437 | archivedate=2008-12-21}}</ref>。

截止至2009年4月13日，電影在美國及加拿大的總票房為83,079,000美元，其他地區約為117,198,951美元，全球總計200,276,784美元<ref name="bom" />。

